<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">        
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon-16x16.png" sizes="16x16" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <title>Super 6 Grille House</title>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/e9f791b4ab.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>  
</head>
<body>
    {{> header Username=Username UserID=id}}

    <div class="reviews-bg">
        <div class="reviews-heading">
            <h1>Reviews from our Customers</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-container">
            <div class="review-box">
                <div class="review-info">
                    <div class="review-user">Javier Soler</div>
                    <p>Great place to order super good, budget-friendly Filipino food. Highly Recommend.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="review-box">
                <div class="review-info">
                    <div class="review-user">Jinky Lim Piche</div>
                    <p>Great food and affordable pricing! ðŸ‘Œ 
                        Great food, Cheap eats, Fast delivery.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="review-box">
                <div class="review-info">
                    <div class="review-user">Joris Avelino</div>
                    <p>Will definitiely order again, food was great and the delivery was quick.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-container">
            <div class="comment-box">
                <h2>Feel Free to Leave Us a Review</h2>
                <form action="/addReview" method="POST">
                    <textarea placeholder="Leave a Review here..." name="review"></textarea>
                    <button class="review-btn">Submit Review</button>
                </form>
                <p>You must have an account in order to leave a review. <a href="/login">Login/Signup</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>